linuxsampler (2.0.0-1+svn1) unreleased; urgency=low

  * Require libgig version >= 4.0.0 as build dependency.
  * Require libasound2-dev or libjack-dev as build dependency.
  * Require dssi-dev as build dependency.
  * Require lv2-dev as build dependency.
  * Suggest qsampler as optional installation.
  * Suggest gigedit as optional installation.
  * Mention QSampler and JSampler/Fantasia in package description.
  * Removed unnecessary dependency to libuuid (originated by libgig's usage
    of it).
  * Assigned linuxsampler-devel@lists.sourceforge.net as maintainer of
    this package.

 -- Christian Schoenebeck <cuse@users.sourceforge.net>  Wed, 06 Apr 2016 19:55:03 +0200

linuxsampler (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New release.
  * liblinuxsampler shared library (liblinuxsampler.so) is now at
    version 4.0.0.
  * Script for building from SVN is now Makefile.svn (Makefile.cvs still
    exists but is deprecated).
  * Updated to Debian compatibility level 7.

 -- Christian Schoenebeck <cuse@users.sourceforge.net>  Wed, 15 Jul 2015 10:29:57 +0200

